Danny,

If you run this in the console on the okd cms  london2012 (jamie/coffee) http://london2012.kitsite.com/kit/console/

It will output a csv file with the data Finn wants  (you'll need to search/replace *** with a line break and save the result as foo.csv)

It works for 50 users but time out when max is set to all (-1) 

Still trying, will try again later, you may need to ask K why it fails 

var criteria = [
    { type: 'Vote' },
    { max: -1}
];
var f = new Finder(criteria);
var results = f.find();   
for (var i=0; i<results.items.length; i++) {
        var p = results.items[i];
        out.writeln(p.owner + ',' + p.getValue('poll')  + ',' + p.getValue('vote') + '***');
}


